snippet.textDisplay: Please do not impose western standards on China. More than 1 million people have died in the US and more than 1 million in Europe.India has more than five million.These countries are capital controlled and have plans to eliminate the low end of the population in order to reduce the social burden.Elected politicians who are also the people feel no guilt.But not China, the Chinese government is an unlimited liability company.Besides, our culture should take good care of the elderly. If grandparents leave, we will lose hope and meaning of life, and the economy will collapse.Our religion in China is actually a mixture of ancestor worship, Taoism, Buddhism and Confucianism.
